{{See also|ASUS DSL series|ASUS}}
===Forum threads=== * [http://www.hwupgrade.it/forum/showthread.php?t=2662095 On '''HWupgrade''']
===Spec. aggregators=== * [http://www.speedguide.net/routers/asus-dsl-n14u-300mbps-wireless-adsl2-router-3294 On '''SpeedGuide.net'''] * [http://www.hwupgrade.it/forum/showthread.php?t=2640545 On '''HWupgrade''']
===Firmware=== :[https://www.asus.com/es/supportonly/DSL-N14U/HelpDesk_Download/ Asus DSL-N14U downloads] :[https://dlcdnets.asus.com/pub/ASUS/wireless/DSL-N14U/FW_DSL-N14U_1123805.zip FW v1.1.2.3_805] :[https://dlcdnets.asus.com/pub/ASUS/wireless/DSL-N14U/GPL_DSL-N14U_1123805.zip FW SRC v1.1.2.3_805]
===Specifications=== :per ''ASUS'''s product page * ''Memory'': 16MB Flash, 64MB (DDR2) RAM * ''Antenna'': 2x Detachable 2dBi antenna * ''Ports'': 4x RJ45 10/100 BaseT for LAN, 1x RJ11 for xDSL *''USB'': 1x USB 2.0 ports * ''Power Adapter'': AC Input: 100~240V (50/60Hz), DC Output: 12V/1A *''Dimensions (W x H x D)'': [[Dimensions::123 mm x 35 mm x 190 mm]] *''Weight'': [[Weight::314 g]]
